<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="updated">Last Updated: March 2026</p>
</div>

<p>
Vexo AI (“we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting
the information processed when you use the <strong>Vexo AI mobile application</strong>.
This Privacy Policy explains how information may be collected, processed, used,
and protected when you use our application.
</p>

<h2>1. Overview</h2>

<p>
Vexo AI is an AI-powered application that allows users to generate videos from
photos, text prompts, or creative inputs.
</p>

<p>
The app may also provide <strong>pre-made video templates and visual styles</strong>
that users can select to create videos more easily.
</p>

<p>
To provide these features, the app may temporarily process certain user-provided
content through secure servers. We aim to minimize the collection and storage of
personal information whenever possible.
</p>

<h2>2. Information We May Process</h2>

<h3>2.1 User Uploaded Content</h3>

<p>
When using video generation features, users may upload or submit content such as:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Images or photos</li>
<li>Text prompts</li>
<li>Video generation instructions</li>
</ul>

<p>
Users may also select from <strong>pre-designed video templates</strong> available
inside the application.
</p>

<p>
This content is used only for generating the requested AI video output.
</p>

<h3>Temporary Processing</h3>

<ul>
<li>Processing usually takes approximately <strong>60 seconds</strong></li>
<li>Uploaded images and prompts are <strong>automatically deleted after processing</strong></li>
<li>Content is <strong>not permanently stored on our servers</strong></li>
</ul>

<p>
We do not use uploaded user content for unrelated purposes.
</p>

<h3>2.2 Generated Video Content</h3>

<p>
When a video is generated, the resulting output is delivered to the user.
Users may choose to save generated videos directly to their own device.
</p>

<h3>2.3 Device and Diagnostic Information</h3>

<p>
To maintain app performance and reliability, limited device information may
be collected automatically such as:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Device model</li>
<li>Operating system version</li>
<li>App version</li>
<li>Crash or diagnostic data</li>
</ul>

<p>
This information helps improve stability and detect technical issues.
</p>

<h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>

<p>Information processed through the app may be used for:</p>

<ul>
<li>Generating AI videos requested by users</li>
<li>Delivering generated results</li>
<li>Improving app performance and stability</li>
<li>Diagnosing technical issues</li>
<li>Maintaining system security</li>
</ul>

<p>
We do <strong>not sell or rent personal information</strong> to third parties.
</p>

<h2>4. Data Retention</h2>

<ul>
<li>Uploaded images and prompts are deleted immediately after processing</li>
<li>Processing usually takes about <strong>60 seconds</strong></li>
<li>Diagnostic data may be retained temporarily to improve service quality</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>
To operate certain features, the app may rely on third-party infrastructure
such as cloud hosting or AI processing providers.
These services may temporarily process information only to perform the
requested functionality.
</p>

<h2>6. Children’s Privacy</h2>

<p>
Vexo AI is <strong>not intended for users under the age of 18</strong>.
</p>

<p>
We do not knowingly collect personal information from individuals under 18.
If we become aware that such information has been provided, we will take
reasonable steps to delete it as soon as possible.
</p>

<p>
Parents or guardians who believe a minor has used the app may contact us.
</p>

<h2>7. Security</h2>

<p>
We implement reasonable technical and administrative measures to protect
information processed through the application. However, no internet-based
service can guarantee absolute security.
</p>

<h2>8. User Control</h2>

<p>
Users control the content they upload and generate within the app.
Users may choose to upload images, provide prompts, generate videos,
and save generated content locally on their device.
</p>

<h2>9. User Generated Content & Templates</h2>

<p>
Vexo AI allows users to upload images, enter prompts, and generate videos
using artificial intelligence. These inputs and outputs may be considered
<strong>user-generated content</strong>.
</p>

<p>Users agree not to generate or upload content that:</p>

<ul>
<li>Violates intellectual property rights</li>
<li>Contains illegal or harmful material</li>
<li>Promotes violence or harassment</li>
<li>Contains explicit or abusive content</li>
<li>Impersonates another person</li>
<li>Violates applicable laws</li>
</ul>

<p>
We reserve the right to restrict or disable access to the service if misuse
is detected.
</p>

<h2>10. Reporting Concerns</h2>

<p>
If you believe content generated through Vexo AI violates these policies,
please contact us:
</p>

<p><strong>Email:</strong> support@vexoai.app</p>

<h2>11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updated versions will
be posted on this page with a revised date.
</p>

<h2>12. Contact</h2>

<p>
For any privacy-related questions, please contact:
</p>

<p><strong>Email:</strong> support@vexoai.app</p>

